0:14:56,000 --> 0:14:58,000
CA: They have a point, Richard.

261
0:14:58,000 --> 0:15:02,000
RB: In fact, I think our airline took a full page ad at the time saying,

262
0:15:02,000 --> 0:15:04,000
you know, come on, Richard,

263
0:15:04,000 --> 0:15:07,000
there are better ways of crossing the Atlantic.

264
0:15:07,000 --> 0:15:08,000
(Laughter)

265
0:15:08,000 --> 0:15:1,000
CA: To do all this,

266
0:15:1,000 --> 0:15:13,000
you must have been a genius from the get-go, right?

