0:15:14,000 --> 0:15:17,000
RB: Well, I won't contradict that.

268
0:15:17,000 --> 0:15:18,000
(Laughter)

269
0:15:18,000 --> 0:15:22,000
CA: OK, this isn't exactly hardball. OK.

270
0:15:22,000 --> 0:15:26,000
Didn't -- weren't you just terrible at school?

271
0:15:26,000 --> 0:15:34,000
RB: I was dyslexic. I had no understanding of schoolwork whatsoever.

272
0:15:37,000 --> 0:15:4,000
